Well, I'm this way, so see ya.

286
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:23,060
Hold it, Junichiro.

287
00:15:23,730 --> 00:15:25,570
Something else you want?

288
00:15:25,570 --> 00:15:29,740
Yes. I want you to call me by
my given name from now on.

289
00:15:30,070 --> 00:15:31,950
