with no future at all...

303
00:16:20,700 --> 00:16:22,710
But I still feel just a bit...

304
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:26,840
The good feelings ended there, though.

305
00:16:27,460 --> 00:16:30,050
Our first date was a bike
ride up a mountain.

306
