436
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:38,680
The truth is I love you,
but I keep beating around the bush

437
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:43,580
We're both the awkward type that'll try to
brush it off as a joke (so much pressure)

438
00:22:43,580 --> 00:22:47,350
Sigh... Getting this exhausted
over nothing is so stupid

439
00:22:47,350 --> 00:22:52,090
We'll never move forward or get
any answers that way, right?

440
00:22:52,090 --> 00:23:00,940
Now you're suddenly grumpy, why all the
swirling emotions? I sense rain coming

441
00:22:52,140 --> 00:22:54,010
