442
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:10,150
You can have my umbrella,
just don't cry or get all mad and soaked

443
00:23:10,150 --> 00:23:14,260
Ah, my broken heart and
broken body are at odds

444
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:18,940
I guess I can't deal with this
unless I put armor on, can I?

445
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:22,890
Constantly losing and being bewitched,
all at your mercy, is just frustrating

446
00:23:22,890 --> 00:23:28,520
I'm gonna solve the riddle of
this impatient, shattering love

447
